<br>
I mean really, can I demand that you follow me around and unlock doors for me?  Oh no, not in my group... I just want to use you like a service.  Maybe you could just hit the mob once to poison it, that'd be great, mm'kay?  I think it's ridiculous you won't follow me around and spend your time and energy as I direct!  I dont care if its against your roleplay, why should that matter?  Its all about the benefit of the rules and I demand you do your thing immediatly.<br>
