Try this one on for size... I'm going to play my character, and my character won't rez certain races or classes.  He's a damn dirty racist.  <br>
<br>
Have I ever, ever, ever rezed someone my character wouldnt?<br>
<br>
I sure have.  I see people get trained, or dye in some none in-game way, Ill shoot them a rez.  Or like at Shintou's ritual, I rezed the people who were sacrificed, (or tried to at least.)<br>
